                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="menarinimaster/components/text"
                            text="&lt;table align=&quot;center&quot;>&#xa;    &lt;tbody>&#xa;        &lt;tr>&#xa;            &lt;td>&lt;img longdesc=&quot;Menarini Group logo&quot; title=&quot;Menarini Group logo&quot; alt=&quot;Menarini Group logo&quot; src=&quot;/Portals/31/Images/notizie/logo_Menarini_group_cs.jpg&quot; />&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td>&#xa;            &lt;td>&lt;img longdesc=&quot;Comune di Firenze&quot; title=&quot;Comune di Firenze&quot; alt=&quot;Comune di Firenze&quot; src=&quot;/Portals/31/Images/notizie/Logo-Comune-Firenze-giglio.jpg&quot; />&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td>&#xa;        &lt;/tr>&#xa;    &lt;/tbody>&#xa;&lt;/table>&#xa;&lt;br />&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;>&lt;strong>&lt;span style=&quot;color: black;&quot;>Press Release&lt;/span>&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;>&lt;strong>&lt;span style=&quot;color: black;&quot;>Ten more &amp;lsquo;comfortable homes&amp;rsquo; renovated by Menarini for ten families hit by the economical crisis. &lt;br />&#xa;First ten completed last year.&lt;/span>&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;>&lt;em>&lt;span style=&quot;color: black;&quot;>Menarini will be renovating ten apartments in the city of Florence as part of their renewed commitment to an initiative in support of the Town Council.&lt;/span>&lt;/em>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;br />&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;>&lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>&lt;em>&lt;span style=&quot;color: black;&quot;>Florence&lt;/span>&lt;/em>&lt;/span>&lt;em>&lt;span style=&quot;color: black;&quot;>, &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>December 12th, 2014&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/em>&lt;span style=&quot;color: black;&quot;> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>&amp;ndash;&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>In the year 2015 Menarini&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>will renew its commitment&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>to support&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>the call for social housing&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>in the city of Florence&lt;/span>, &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>by renovating, &lt;/span>at their own expense,&lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;> a further&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>10&lt;/span> apartments belonging to &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>the town council and &lt;/span>taking care &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>of the work involved&lt;/span>.&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;>&lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot; style=&quot;color: black;&quot;>As early Spring&lt;/span>&lt;span style=&quot;color: black;&quot;>&amp;nbsp; &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>2015&lt;/span>, &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>&quot;&lt;/span>10 &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>apartments&lt;/span>&quot; &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>will be&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>fully&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>renovated and ready to be handed over to&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>families who have lost their homes as a consequence of not being able to pay&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>their rent&lt;/span> due&lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;> to economic difficulties&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>brought on by the crisis.&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;>&lt;span style=&quot;color: black;&quot;>&lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>For&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>the second consecutive year, and in a period in which social housing represents a significant&amp;nbsp; concern&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>for&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span>F&lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>lorence&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>and &amp;nbsp;other major&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>cities in Italy,&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>Menarini has chosen to&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>confirm&lt;/span> its &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>commitment&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>to the City&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>of Florence&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>with an undertaking of deep&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>symbolic value&lt;/span>.&amp;nbsp; &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>The project&lt;/span>, which will be carried out &amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>in collaboration with&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>Casa&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>S.P.A.&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>(the organisation which takes care of matters pertaining to public housing&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>in the Florentine area&lt;/span>), foresees the restoration of the&lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;> electrical&lt;/span>, &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>mechanical&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>and thermo&lt;/span>&lt;span class=&quot;atn&quot;>-&lt;/span>sanitary systems, the replacing of the tiles in the &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>kitchens and&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>bathrooms&lt;/span>, &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>the repair or replacement of windows&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>in 10&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>apartments located in the city&amp;rsquo;s &lt;/span>&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>2&lt;/span>, &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>3 and&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>5 districts.&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>The families who will be receiving the keys to these homes are needy families who have already registered in the town council&amp;rsquo;s waiting lists. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;>&lt;img longdesc=&quot;The Mayor of Florence, Dario Nardella, the Town counsellor for  Social Housing, Sara Funaro, Chairman and Vice Chairman of the Menarini Pharmaceutical group, Lucia and Alberto Giovanni Aleotti, along with the President of Casa Spa, Luca Talluri&quot; title=&quot;The Mayor of Florence, Dario Nardella, the Town counsellor for  Social Housing, Sara Funaro, Chairman and Vice Chairman of the Menarini Pharmaceutical group, Lucia and Alberto Giovanni Aleotti, along with the President of Casa Spa, Luca Talluri&quot; alt=&quot;The Mayor of Florence, Dario Nardella, the Town counsellor for  Social Housing, Sara Funaro, Chairman and Vice Chairman of the Menarini Pharmaceutical group, Lucia and Alberto Giovanni Aleotti, along with the President of Casa Spa, Luca Talluri&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot; src=&quot;/Portals/31/Images/notizie/Comunicato_stampa_12DIC2014.jpg&quot; />&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;>&lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot; style=&quot;color: black;&quot;>The Mayor&lt;/span>&lt;span style=&quot;color: black;&quot;> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>of Florence&lt;/span>, &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>&lt;strong>Dario&lt;/strong>&lt;/span>&lt;strong> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>Nardella&lt;/span>&lt;/strong>, &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>the Town counsellor for &amp;nbsp;Social Housing&lt;/span>, &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>&lt;strong>Sara&lt;/strong>&lt;/span>&lt;strong> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>Funaro&lt;/span>&lt;/strong>, &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>Chairman and Vice Chairman&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>of the&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>Menarini Pharmaceutical group&lt;/span>&lt;strong>, &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>Lucia&lt;/span> &lt;strong style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;>Aleotti&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong>&lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>and&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>Alberto&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>Giovanni&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>Aleotti&lt;/span>&lt;/strong>, along with the &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>President&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>of&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>Casa Spa&lt;/span>, &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>&lt;strong>Luca&lt;/strong>&lt;/span>&lt;strong> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>Talluri&lt;/span>&lt;/strong>, &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>illustrated the project&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>during a&lt;/span> &lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot;>press conference held this morning in Florence&amp;rsquo;s Town Hall (Palazzo Vecchio).&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>"
                            textIsRich="true"/>
